: <MARK ( --- addr )
\G Mark a backward reference.
  HERE ;

: <RESOLVE ( addr ---)
\G Resolve a backward reference.
  , ;

: >MARK ( --- addr )
\G Mark a forward reference.
  HERE 0 , ;

: >RESOLVE ( addr --- )
\G Resolve a forward reference.
  HERE SWAP ! ;


: MODE 22 EMIT EMIT ;
: CURSOR 23 EMIT 1 EMIT EMIT 0 EMIT 0 EMIT 0 EMIT 0 EMIT 0 EMIT 0 EMIT 0 EMIT ;

: 2EMIT ( u1 u2 ---)
\G Emits u2 followed by u1.
    EMIT EMIT ;


: VDU ( "name" --- mark) 
\G Loop over all placed C, and , values placed before the following END-VDU.
    !CSP CREATE >MARK DOES> DUP @ SWAP CELL+ DO
	I C@ EMIT LOOP ;
	
: VDUDG ( c "name" ---)
\G Makes a VDU header for the character on the stack
    DUP 32 < OVER 127 = OR IF DROP -21 THROW THEN \ Error. 
    >R VDU R> 23 C, C, ; \ Make UDG header. 
	
: END-VDU ( mark ---)
\G End a VDU definition which then has a name to use.
    >RESOLVE ?CSP ; 

: COL ( col ---)
\G Set text colour.
    17 2EMIT ;

: VWAIT
  16 MS ;

: WAVE 2DROP ;
: VOL 2DROP ;


